If you are a salsa fan, this salsa stuffed chicken breasts recipe is perfect for you.  These stuffed chicken breasts are super filling, and can be enjoyed on their own or with a light portion of fresh green salad. For a more filling and hearty meal, serve these delicious and tender chicken breasts with a side portion of creamy mash potatoes, fluffy rice or steamed bread.  ALSO TRY: Recipe of the day: Hearty South African macaroni and mince recipe This recipe was found on foodandwine.com